      %h3 OUR DIRECT TRADE MISSION
      %p We specialize in direct trade coffee by working with artisan roasters who have direct relationships with coffee farmers. Our partner roasters support small-scale coffee farms by paying more than fair trade prices and working with the farmers to improve their farming practices and quality of their coffee. We pass on the story of the coffee to you - from the farm to your cup.
